thread.title: Apple Music has 6.5 million paid subscribers

author: Chronicle News Services
title: Apple Music has 6.5 million paid subscribers
text: Apple Music already has 6.5 million paid subscribers, or about a third of the 20 million who pay for industry rival Spotify, after only four months on the market, according to Apple Chief Executive Officer Tim Cook, who spoke at a conference Monday night.
